videos.description: Admiral Schofield swoops in and blocks Florida's Kevarrius Hayes' dunk.
videos.headline: Schofield flies in for a big rejection

videos.description: Admiral Schofield slings a skip pass to an open Lamonte Turner for a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Schofield's sweet cross-court pass sets up 3

videos.description: Lamonte Turner steals the ball and is rewarded with a one-handed slam.
videos.headline: Turner's steal leads to easy dunk

videos.description: Grant Williams strides down the lane and throws down a massive one-handed slam dunk.
videos.headline: Williams throws down a hammering dunk

videos.description: Florida's Kevarrius Hayes catches lob from Andrew Nembhard and throws it down.
videos.headline: Hayes throws down alley-oop

videos.description: Tennessee's Grant Williams finds Admiral Schofield for a dagger 3-pointer in the corner to lock up a win over Florida.
videos.headline: Grant finds Schofield for dagger 3

videos.description: Grant Williams and Admiral Schofield both 'Gator chomp' walking off the court after an 11-point win at Florida.
videos.headline: Tennessee players  'Gator Chomp' after win in Gainesville
